UPDATE tours SET description = 'Discover the wonders of Dubai with an exclusive tour that will take you among the most iconic places of this extraordinary city, where the past meets the future. Accompanied by an expert Italian guide, you will live an authentic experience among imposing skyscrapers, historic markets and breathtaking views.

