UPDATE tours SET description = 'Our day begins with an extraordinary experience at the Bahrain Formula 1 Circuit (BIC), one of the most advanced and spectacular in the world. If you choose the VIP tour, you will have exclusive access to the prestigious media room, you can visit the control tower and walk some sections of the track experiencing the excitement of Formula 1 up close. An unmissable opportunity for motorsport enthusiasts!

