UPDATE tours SET description = 'The adventure begins with pick-up directly from the ship aboard a 4x4 jeep. We leave behind the hustle and bustle of the city as we head towards the heart of Dubai''s desert, an endless expanse of golden sand. Before venturing onto the dunes, you will have the opportunity to take a Quad or Dune Buggy ride (paid activities).

